    <subject> data model </subject>
    <subject> coordinate system </subject>
    <description>
        This document provides a complete design description of the
        Space-Time Coordinate (STC) metadata for the Virtual
        Observatory. It explains the various components, highlights
        some implementation considerations, presents a complete set of
        UML diagrams, and discusses the relation between STC and
        certain other parts of the Data Model. Two serializations are
        discussed: XML Schema (STC-X) and String (STC-S); the former
        is an integral part of this Recommendation. 
      </description>
